snippet: The police said the Pakistani government’s lead prosecutor in a case involving the assassination of former Prime Minister Benazir Bhutto has been shot to death.
abstract: Chaudhry Zulfikar, lead prosecutor investigating assassination of former Prime Min Benazir Bhutto, is shot to death while driving to court; former military ruler Pervez Musharraf has been implicated in case.
lead_paragraph: The police said the Pakistani government’s lead prosecutor in a case involving the assassination of former Prime Minister Benazir Bhutto has been shot to death.

headline.main: Pakistan: Prosecutor in Case of Former Ruler Shot Dead
headline.print_headline: Pakistan: Prosecutor in Case Of Former Ruler Shot Dead
